Anup,

You do need Python to process .cti files.  Also, the build procedure 
runs a couple of Python scripts.
It seems &#39;configure&#39; could not find python on your system.  RedHat 
linux should come with python preinstalled, but it may appear as 
&#39;python2&#39;. Make sure python is on the path, or else define environment 
variable PYTHON_CMD to equal the full pathname for python, and then run 
&#39;configure&#39; again.

Dave


